sal additive structure on $K^*\\cup\\{0\\}$ and hence a non-zero meromorphic\nfunction on $X$ is given by a universal additive expression which is\nindependent of the ring structure of $K(X)^*\\cup\\{0\\}$ (this is also inspired\nby Mochizuki's results on Theta functions). Also see Theorem 7.6.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 04:31:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Aug 2019 16:45:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 Dec 2019 16:15:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-11"}
