 oxygen p-states. The bonding\nnature of this material has also been addressed using DOS which is further\nverified through the electron charge density plot. Though the optical\nproperties of this material are found to be anisotropic but optical isotropy\ncan be seen in lower energy value.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 09:41:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-18"}
